OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteve Coogan says Jimmy    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSavile drama The Reckoning 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'will vindicate itself'    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steve Coogan has said a TV drama in    
OL,6, which he plays Jimmy Savile is "walking
OL,7, a tightrope" but will "vindicate       
OL,8, itself" when it reaches screens.       
OL,10,FCoogan will be seen later this year as 
OL,11,Fthe TV presenter and serial abuser in  
OL,12,FBBC One's The Reckoning.               
OL,14,F"People have a sort of revulsion about 
OL,15,Fthe idea of even making it," the actor 
OL,16,Ftold BBC Radio 5 Live.                 
OL,18,F"But in actual fact, it's a mistake to 
OL,19,Fthink that the best way to deal with   
OL,20,Fsomething is to not talk about it."    
